The files located in this directory are generated by running the following commands:

cpk -setup gmail.com
cpk -genkey alice@gmail.com > alice.pem
cpk -set-identity alice@gmail.com
cpk -import-sign-key -in alice.pem

The private key password is "1".

The -imort-sign-key operation might fail most of the time. But it can success after trying several times....

Sign:
echo hi > doc.txt
cpk -sign < doc.txt > doc.txt.sig

Verify:
cpk -verify $(cat doc.txt.sig) < doc.txt -signer alice@gmail.com

The verification usually fail due to unstability of signing operation. (It must be a bug)  But trying serveral times can make it success....
